name: New Year's Day
description: January  1  marks  the  beginning  of  the  official  New  Year  in  Pakistan  and  is celebrated throughout the country as New Year 2019s Day

name: Kashmir Day
description: Kashmir Solidarity Day is annually observed in Pakistan on February 5 to express solidarity with the people of Jammu and Kashmir. It also honors the sacrifices made for Kashmir\u2019s liberation.
